      "side": 1,
      "message": "While this is correct for rbh-find, it isn\u0027t for other sources that use a struct filters_context, such as the GC, report or the policy engine, and I\u0027d rather not assume that all backends have been correctly initialized (which is the reason for this fix anyway). As Guillaume said, I\u0027d rather have a continue here instead.",
